273
00:18:56.041 --> 00:18:57.833
Ask it to search
for active agents.

274
00:18:57.916 --> 00:18:59.333
Search active agents.

275
00:18:59.416 --> 00:19:01.708
The X Case is the only tech
that can locate

276
00:19:01.791 --> 00:19:03.833
